PrecisOrder Amending the ORDER DECLARING AN AMNESTY PERIOD (2006) - which extends the amnesty period protecting individuals from incurring criminal liability under the Criminal Code as a result of the illegal possession of unregistered non-restricted firearms, for one year, i.e., from May 16, 2007 to May 16, 2008.
